00:00:31.728 --> 00:00:53.733
I stand by that when I tell you I saw Jesus standing here when he visited me and told me that we needed to pray for President Trump's life, that his life was in danger, and that if anything was to happen to President Trump, he was holding the church accountable by our prayer of intercession concerning his life.

00:00:58.719 --> 00:01:07.760
I believe wholeheartedly the church has power and authority.

00:01:08.103 --> 00:01:31.119
As we rise up as believing believers, not doubters, and stand as watchmen, as the Lord reveals the things the enemy has planned, just like he did the first time, I saw precisely where the bullet would go.

00:01:31.119 --> 00:01:32.464
It was to the tee.

00:01:32.464 --> 00:01:34.891
I saw the blood flowing and I thought it busted his eardrum.

00:01:34.891 --> 00:01:41.013
Everyone wants you to go over the visions, and I am trying to describe what the Lord is showing me.

00:01:53.439 --> 00:02:00.514
We will continue to pray for President Trump and his safety concerning finishing his term.

00:02:00.514 --> 00:02:07.280
Now, I know there have been people who believe that I missed it, and that is fine.

00:02:07.620 --> 00:02:08.949
You know what, folks?

00:02:08.949 --> 00:02:12.650
If Brandon Biggs misses it, I will be the first one to come out and tell you.

00:02:12.650 --> 00:02:18.696
I do not hide from them like some people who try to pull their videos down and hide them because they do not want to be embarrassed.

00:02:20.205 --> 00:02:22.495
I am human; I miss it.

00:02:25.897 --> 00:02:27.650
Is Brandon Biggs a prophet?

00:02:28.520 --> 00:02:29.100
I am a watchman.

00:02:29.850 --> 00:02:31.500
I come on here and I pray with you all.

00:02:31.500 --> 00:02:35.472
The Lord said, I have called you to go on YouTube and pray.

00:02:50.690 --> 00:02:50.900
That is what we come here to do.

00:02:51.950 --> 00:02:53.040
I am not here to be a showboat.

00:02:58.950 --> 00:02:59.180
I deflect always to him.

00:02:59.180 --> 00:03:01.657
He does not use me, he uses me.

00:03:08.280 --> 00:03:16.169
If there is something I have missed and I tell you that Jesus has appeared to me and told me to pray for President Trump and that there was an attempt, I can tell you exactly what the man looks like.

00:03:17.164 --> 00:03:22.160
I have already told the people in authority about all of it and they said it was accurate.

00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:32.360
Regardless if people say it is false, I have people high in the government who said it was accurate because of the things they have had tips on.

00:03:39.778 --> 00:03:40.062
I cannot go into the depth about it because that would be foolish.

00:03:42.200 --> 00:03:45.972
To people who say it is false, you are ignorant; you have no idea what you are talking about.

00:03:57.111 --> 00:03:57.448
I realize that some people just want clicks for views because their view count is down, so they throw things out there to get higher view counts.

00:03:57.448 --> 00:04:03.680
They play around with stuff and that is okay, but I have to rise above it.

00:04:03.680 --> 00:04:11.049
I know beyond a shadow of a doubt God has called us for such a time as this to pray for the nations.

00:04:13.760 --> 00:04:17.359
If we do not, I believe the enemy will come in and wreak havoc.

00:04:20.933 --> 00:04:31.747
As long as we have a backbone like a crowbar and we stand on the Word, we are the salt and the light and we can change things through prayer.

00:04:31.747 --> 00:04:39.582
If we bow down to the demonic, they will run right over us as we see in New York.

00:04:39.582 --> 00:04:47.199
They got what they voted for.

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:03.830
I have seen great fires; I have seen buildings on the 41st floor.

00:05:03.830 --> 00:05:08.507
We have seen a lot with what the Lord showed us this last video.

00:05:08.507 --> 00:05:15.208
He told us about praying for these gas plants and the seven employees with the white helmets praying over these people.

00:05:15.208 --> 00:05:17.048
There were layers to this explosion.

00:05:23.280 --> 00:05:27.131
When I was looking into that vision, I thought it was a massive nuclear device going off in the middle of the field.

00:05:46.686 --> 00:05:46.903
The Lord said, Brandon, do not always assume that is nuclear.

00:05:53.840 --> 00:05:54.220
It looked like it, but it was a major explosion.

00:06:11.200 --> 00:06:13.102
That is why we are praying over Louisiana, praying over these gas plants, praying over Tuttle, Oklahoma, and these major events that I believe could be false flag or black swan events.

00:06:13.102 --> 00:06:15.520
We will continue to pray over that.

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:18.680
The other thing the Lord showed us was Macron.

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:23.939
I saw him devising a plan again to silence an individual.

00:06:28.107 --> 00:06:30.320
I saw a cliff and I saw that woman's face.

00:06:30.320 --> 00:06:35.531
I try not to talk about people because I do not want the drama.

00:06:43.460 --> 00:06:43.800
I saw another alternative media television face and I will say his name.

00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:49.938
I believe Alex Jones has a major call on his life.

00:06:50.711 --> 00:06:56.391
I believe it is very prophetic for the end times, calling out the deep state and this dark agenda.

00:07:11.599 --> 00:07:12.292
I believe his life is something we should pray for.

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:21.369
I saw a crossbow and an arrow.

00:07:38.719 --> 00:07:39.280
The Lord said, remember when I prayed over this before, he would be like a new John the Baptist in these end times, his voice would get louder, and he would start to proclaim Christianity and salvation in Jesus' return.

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:46.685
I saw a black-tipped arrow that looked like razor blades coming out of a crossbow.

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:00.080
I do not know where this was, but I saw it coming out of the side of a van as it was driving away.

00:08:00.080 --> 00:08:01.538
It was silent.

00:08:01.538 --> 00:08:10.906
If anybody is familiar with hunting with a crossbow, it makes a noise, but it is nothing compared to a firearm.

00:08:13.479 --> 00:08:16.020
That is why the Lord said you need to pray for him.

00:08:16.020 --> 00:08:24.491
There will be an attempt and I will spare his life and he will become more radical for me in the days ahead.

00:08:26.900 --> 00:08:31.733
I believe with all my heart that Alex Jones will become one of the greatest mouthpieces for Jesus in the days ahead.

00:08:39.099 --> 00:08:39.520
The same with the Kardashians and Justin Bieber.

00:08:39.520 --> 00:08:48.879
Justin Bieber looks like he is going through a lot, but I believe God has a major call on him and he will be used even greater.

00:08:48.879 --> 00:08:55.360
Mel Gibson, we have to pray for him regarding the Passion of Christ 2 movie.

00:08:55.360 --> 00:09:08.560
Braden put out the video today, the short about this nasty ringworm thing that is happening all over with 30 cases.

00:09:09.320 --> 00:09:11.280
