00:09:12.516 --> 00:09:23.800
Do you have that son where you can play just that clip without having the short, or do you have that where you could replay that of what the Lord specifically said?

00:09:23.800 --> 00:09:25.680
Did you upload that?

00:09:35.420 --> 00:09:37.243
Well, if you don't, that's fine.

00:09:37.243 --> 00:09:39.235
But I brought it out.

00:09:39.235 --> 00:09:43.000
I didn't realize when I gave the word I was a lot skinnier there.

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:53.146
But as of April 30th, 2025, the Lord spoke to us, and it was when Carney was getting elected.

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:57.017
I told you I saw Justin Trudeau coming out.

