00:10:13.233 --> 00:10:20.297
He said the majority would vote that way, and the balance of it would be weighed this way.

00:10:20.663 --> 00:10:25.710
Because of the balance of where people were voting, they were voting for corruption.

00:10:35.080 --> 00:10:35.493
There is a gnat flying around here, sorry, I get distracted.

00:10:58.480 --> 00:10:58.750
But because they would vote that way, they were voting for immoral things, homosexuality, etc.

00:10:58.750 --> 00:11:04.080
Because of this, it would open up doors and this plague would come out of it.

00:11:05.389 --> 00:11:19.400
It would evolve like how you get certain drugs when you have a virus or something; your body becomes immune to certain things because of the medicine that they are giving, and it becomes resistant in the strain.

00:11:19.400 --> 00:11:25.600
I saw that this thing would come up because of the kids being trafficked.

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:33.024
The Lord was ticked off and said, "They have messed with the kids.

00:11:33.024 --> 00:11:37.500
" You will hear it here if Braden can get it up.

00:11:37.910 --> 00:11:39.884
It was about the children.

00:11:47.519 --> 00:11:57.252
I saw it spreading all throughout Asia, and this virus would become so much infection in the groin area that they could not take care of it and they had to amputate, like gangrene.

00:11:57.252 --> 00:12:02.560
Whenever gangrene sets in through blood sugar problems, this is what I saw happening in a man's genitalia.

00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:08.377
It was so much infection that they had to amputate that out of there.

00:12:08.377 --> 00:12:18.160
There was no way of fixing it, and it made them so sick it eventually took their life.

00:12:18.160 --> 00:12:20.480
Now, are we at that level?

00:12:35.511 --> 00:12:35.867
No.

00:12:35.867 --> 00:12:39.244
Am I seeing the beginning stages of something?

00:12:51.547 --> 00:12:55.279
I truly believe we are seeing something on April 30th.

00:12:55.279 --> 00:12:56.759
Is it something new?

00:12:56.759 --> 00:12:58.800
Now, do you have it, son?

00:12:58.800 --> 00:12:59.120
Yeah.

00:12:59.120 --> 00:13:00.231
You can play it now.

00:13:00.676 --> 00:13:02.987
I want to go over these words.

00:13:02.987 --> 00:13:12.870
This is almost a year ago.

00:13:13.413 --> 00:13:27.413
I saw a new type of STD, a new venereal disease that had never been seen before, coming through certain practices that are ungodly.

00:13:27.413 --> 00:13:40.137
And because of these ungodly acts, because of the reprobate mind of wanting to go this way, the scales in the spirit realm were weighed and they were found lacking.

00:13:40.137 --> 00:13:43.360
And this goes for America also.

00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:50.359
It infiltrated into New York, Boston, these major cities.

00:13:50.359 --> 00:13:56.220
A new venereal disease that has never been known before.

00:13:56.220 --> 00:14:08.765
