The anger of the Lord was so strong; I thought I was going to vibrate out of my car as he spoke.

00:14:33.280 --> 00:14:38.124
The anger was like the thunder above my heavens right now.

00:14:38.124 --> 00:14:42.899
It was that loud as I hear the rain and the hail.

00:15:01.893 --> 00:15:02.560
It was very strong, the rebuke and the warning coming from the Father.

00:15:02.560 --> 00:15:16.112
He told me because of these things that you are seeing, decisions have been made and you will see a judgment.

00:15:16.112 --> 00:15:22.380
As we see the beginning stages of this new virus, and it is nasty, is it going to morph?

00:15:22.380 --> 00:15:25.672
Is it going to get more and more?

00:15:32.549 --> 00:15:32.800
I believe it will.

00:15:32.800 --> 00:15:34.560
How long does it take?

00:15:34.560 --> 00:15:35.867
I don't know.

00:15:35.867 --> 00:15:41.039
I never know when I am praying in the spirit and the Lord shows me things and dates.

00:15:53.700 --> 00:16:08.940
I talked to one elder who said if you want prophetic ministry, because we see in part and we hear in part, never give dates that often unless you really feel instructed by the Holy Spirit because there is depth perception to it.

00:16:08.940 --> 00:16:09.897
I am learning.

00:16:09.897 --> 00:16:11.040
Depth perception is huge.

00:16:13.383 --> 00:16:21.324
It looks like a lot of times it is right in front of my face, like it is going to happen tomorrow.

00:16:21.324 --> 00:16:30.610
Sometimes I tell Braden and Diana after the broadcast is over, I will be looking for this tomorrow in the news.

00:16:38.959 --> 00:16:39.393
That is how imminent it felt.

00:16:41.566 --> 00:16:52.141
There are some things you see a year before this even starts to happen in a little bit on the news, like nasty sores on people's faces.

00:16:52.141 --> 00:16:59.640
At that time, it looked like it was right there, like it is going to happen right then.

00:16:59.640 --> 00:17:11.760
We are going to look at it, we are going to turn on the news tomorrow, and it does not happen that way because I realized there is a difference in the spirit realm when you are praying over things.

00:17:11.760 --> 00:17:13.679
God is not in a hurry.

00:17:17.219 --> 00:17:17.549
I just stay to my little thing here.

00:17:17.549 --> 00:17:19.537
I don't go to the conferences.

00:17:24.080 --> 00:17:24.480
I am so thankful for all of you that have invited me.

00:17:25.866 --> 00:17:30.620
I just got an invite to come to South Korea and preach a conference, and that is real tempting.

00:17:46.820 --> 00:17:47.200
I told Braden, "Man, Dad, that would be kind of cool to go preach in South Korea.

00:17:55.760 --> 00:17:56.080
" That is the only one I can tell you that I have been really leaning towards.

