We're the clay.

01:24:10.852 --> 01:24:12.468
I have a treasure in earthen vessels that the excellency of the power is known of him and not of me.

01:24:12.468 --> 01:24:13.383
He controls it.

01:24:17.280 --> 01:24:24.382
But I want you to know my friend, he's a friend that sticks closer than a brother.

01:24:24.382 --> 01:24:32.900
He'll never leave you and he'll never forsake you.

01:24:32.900 --> 01:24:36.944
Lo, unto the end of the earth, he'll be with you always.

01:24:36.944 --> 01:24:46.239
But if you're here tonight and you've never asked Jesus Christ to be your Lord and personal Savior, tonight's your night.

01:24:46.239 --> 01:24:47.920
It's appointed unto man once to die.

01:24:47.920 --> 01:24:48.560
Once.

01:24:48.560 --> 01:24:49.840
There's no reincarnation.

01:24:49.840 --> 01:25:02.940
There's the Asian channel always asking me, "Brandon, do you not believe in reincarnation?

01:25:02.940 --> 01:25:03.700
" No.

01:25:15.280 --> 01:25:15.550
That is false.

01:25:15.550 --> 01:25:16.900
It's a false doctrine.

01:25:16.900 --> 01:25:18.020
That's a lie.

01:25:18.020 --> 01:25:20.240
You don't come back as a butterfly.

01:25:20.240 --> 01:25:22.280
You don't come back as a dog.

01:25:22.280 --> 01:25:30.140
No, there's appointed unto man once to die and after that the judgment.

01:25:30.140 --> 01:25:41.440
You will stand before the Lord and give an account of every idle word, everything that you've spoken, every thought.

01:25:44.994 --> 01:26:03.360
I'm telling you I want to be on the side of grace and mercy because I've confessed Jesus Christ as my Lord and my personal savior and I say, "Jesus, forgive me.

01:26:03.360 --> 01:26:03.520
Jesus, forgive me.

01:26:04.640 --> 01:26:05.120
I need you.

01:26:18.719 --> 01:26:19.359
I can't do this life without you.

01:26:20.819 --> 01:26:22.587
I need you to be the captain of my ship.

01:26:35.520 --> 01:26:36.710
I need you to be the one that is leading me and guiding me and helping me in all my decisions.

01:26:36.710 --> 01:26:37.840
I can't do this without you.

01:26:39.280 --> 01:26:54.192
" There are many of you that have gone your whole life thinking that there's no God, that you just go into nothingness.

01:26:54.192 --> 01:26:56.350
But you're wrong.

01:26:56.350 --> 01:27:05.355
You're gambling with eternity by an assumption.

01:27:05.355 --> 01:27:23.428
Look all around you at the stars that have been thrown into space.

01:27:23.428 --> 01:27:26.846
Look at the sand.

01:27:26.846 --> 01:27:35.653
Look at the water that comes in.

01:27:35.653 --> 01:27:38.920
Look at the trees.

01:27:38.920 --> 01:27:43.540
Look at the birds.

01:27:43.540 --> 01:27:50.453
Look at everything around you and say there's no God.

01:27:50.453 --> 01:27:51.253
How foolish.

01:27:51.253 --> 01:27:53.737
We are fearfully and wonderfully made and we're made in his image.

01:27:53.737 --> 01:28:33.667
If you look at our blood veins, our highway of blood veins that go through us that keep us alive, our heart, how we're created in our mother's womb, we're born into this earth out of a microscopic seed of a sperm that hits an egg, and look at the beauty of life how it all happens and we say there's no God.

01:28:59.672 --> 01:29:00.320
I want to introduce you to my friend.

01:29:00.320 --> 01:29:04.868
There is a God.

01:29:19.485 --> 01:29:19.908
And he'll become so real to you the moment you invite him into your heart.

01:29:24.540 --> 01:29:34.667
The moment you confess your sins, he is faithful and just to forgive you of your sins and cleanse you of all unrighteousness.

01:29:34.667 --> 01:29:38.960
There's a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

01:29:38.960 --> 01:29:46.239
I've heard it so many times, but this is really true.

01:29:46.239 --> 01:29:52.159
I want to ask you, do you know my friend?

01:29:52.159 --> 01:29:54.834
Or maybe you've known him.

01:29:54.834 --> 01:30:11.451
Maybe you had a relationship with Jesus at one point in time and you've fallen back and you've backslidden.

01:30:19.280 --> 01:30:19.760
You're not totally cold.

01:30:19.760 --> 01:30:21.840
You're just lukewarm.

01:30:21.840 --> 01:30:33.400
And the Bible says he'd rather you be hot or cold.

01:30:33.400 --> 01:30:41.279
If you're lukewarm, he'll spew you out of his mouth.

01:30:41.279 --> 01:30:50.840
But I want you to make the decision tonight to be all-in for Jesus.

01:30:55.005 --> 01:31:00.457
To sell out, to say, "Jesus, I'm not going to do this life without you.

01:31:00.457 --> 01:31:02.480
I don't want to.

01:31:02.480 --> 01:31:09.104
I want you to be the Lord of my life.

01:31:09.104 --> 01:31:21.199
" Stop hanging around the people that keep pulling you down.

01:31:21.199 --> 01:31:42.680
Make a choice tonight to maybe separate yourself from folks and say, "Listen, I choose to follow Jesus today and I'm not going back to the sin I used to walk in.

01:31:52.948 --> 01:32:01.509
" The prodigal son was in the pig pen and he thought, "Man, if I can just go back and be a servant in my father's house, maybe I could just do that.

01:32:01.509 --> 01:32:09.040
" And so because he had spent all his inheritance, he had big wild parties.

01:32:09.040 --> 01:32:12.159
He was having a good old time.

01:32:12.159 --> 01:32:15.600
But then he had spent everything.

01:32:15.600 --> 01:32:18.259
He was in a pig pen.

01:32:40.605 --> 01:32:40.994
But what was amazing was his father had a robe and he was ready to kill the fatted calf when he saw him coming.

01:32:43.154 --> 01:32:45.234
And that's what the Lord's doing for you right now.

01:32:45.234 --> 01:32:47.840
He's ready to kill the fatted calf.

01:32:47.840 --> 01:32:50.987
He says, "My son, my daughter's home tonight.

01:32:50.987 --> 01:33:02.056
" God didn't turn his back on you, you turned your back on him, but tonight's your night to turn back and say, "I want to make everything right in my life.

01:33:13.400 --> 01:33:13.680
" So, I want you to be bold about your decision before we move on.

01:33:13.680 --> 01:33:28.137
And I want you to say, "Brandon, I want to be saved," or, "I'm coming home tonight.

01:33:46.360 --> 01:33:46.730
" And if that's you, and this is speaking and you feel that tugging on your heart, you feel that knocking on your heart right now, that's the Holy Spirit.

01:33:51.109 --> 01:33:52.880
The Bible says that no man comes to the father unless he's called by him.

01:33:52.880 --> 01:33:59.648
He's drawing on you and right now he's pulling on you and he's saying, "Will you come home?

01:33:59.648 --> 01:34:05.369
" So, I'm going to say a simple little prayer that a 5-year-old could say and believe.

01:34:05.369 --> 01:34:07.590
It doesn't have to be all religious.

01:34:07.590 --> 01:34:09.485
I hate religion, but I love relationship.

01:34:09.770 --> 01:34:11.501
And I love my friend Jesus.

01:34:11.501 --> 01:34:13.920
What a friend we have in Jesus.

01:34:24.960 --> 01:34:25.280
And that's true to me.

01:34:25.280 --> 01:34:29.120
Say, "Jesus, I believe you're the son of God.

01:34:29.120 --> 01:34:34.033
I believe you died for me and you rose again on the third day.

01:34:35.450 --> 01:34:40.330
Jesus, I ask you to forgive me of my sins.

01:34:40.330 --> 01:34:43.326
Wash me with your precious blood today.

01:34:43.326 --> 01:34:46.660
Today, Lord, I turn my back on the world.

01:34:46.660 --> 01:34:49.460
I turn my back on the devil.

01:35:17.108 --> 01:35:17.496
I turn my back on my sin.

01:35:21.679 --> 01:35:22.033
And from this day forward, Lord, I'll serve you.

01:35:22.033 --> 01:35:27.520
I ask you to write my name in the Lamb's book of life.

01:35:27.520 --> 01:35:31.360
Thank you, Lord, that you forgive me of my sins.

01:35:31.360 --> 01:35:35.440
Thank you, Lord, that my name is written in that Lamb's book of life.

01:35:35.440 --> 01:35:36.811
Thank you, Lord.

01:35:36.811 --> 01:35:43.710
From this day forward, I'll serve you with all I have.

01:35:43.710 --> 01:35:45.029
I'm all in.

01:35:45.029 --> 01:35:49.653
If I die today, Lord, I'll be with you in paradise forevermore.

01:35:49.653 --> 01:35:56.596
Thank you, Lord, that I'm no longer a sinner, but I am a sinner that's saved by grace.

01:35:56.596 --> 01:35:58.389
I'm no longer a sinner.

01:35:58.389 --> 01:36:02.560
I might sin, but I'm not going to live in sin.

01:36:02.560 --> 01:36:03.609
" There is a difference.

01:36:05.920 --> 01:36:08.490
You can mess up, but I am not doing it willfully.

01:36:08.490 --> 01:36:10.213
I am not choosing to.

01:36:10.213 --> 01:36:13.823
People mess up like I did a couple of days ago.

01:36:13.823 --> 01:36:18.551
People mess up, but when you do, you run to God when you sin.

01:36:18.551 --> 01:36:20.680
You do not run away from him.

01:36:22.907 --> 01:36:29.160
And the moment you confess it is not when the Lord found out about it; it is when you got rid of it.

01:36:29.160 --> 01:36:37.280
If you fall down and scrape your knee, you stand up and say, "Jesus, I thank you that I am free.

01:36:37.280 --> 01:36:45.143
" So, if you just said that prayer, I believe you just got born again.

01:36:45.143 --> 01:36:49.277
Welcome to the family.

01:36:49.277 --> 01:36:55.993
Now, what do you do?

01:36:55.993 --> 01:36:58.947
Go to a non-denominational church.

01:36:58.947 --> 01:37:08.560
There are good ones, like the Church of His Presence, John Kilpatrick.

01:37:08.560 --> 01:37:18.479
I would go down to that one if I was in that area.

01:37:18.479 --> 01:37:23.920
Or our church, Collinsville Glorious Church.

01:37:23.920 --> 01:37:27.040
There are good churches around.

01:37:58.000 --> 01:37:58.650
You just have to find them.

01:37:58.650 --> 01:38:00.600
Non-denominational churches.

01:38:00.600 --> 01:38:04.240
Go to those churches.

01:38:04.240 --> 01:38:07.669
Tell them, "I want to be water baptized.

01:38:28.550 --> 01:38:28.900
I got born again listening to a guy on YouTube and I want to be water baptized.

01:38:28.900 --> 01:38:30.789
" Get water baptized.

01:38:30.789 --> 01:38:34.780
Come over here and pray with us.

01:38:34.780 --> 01:38:54.112
Go to their Wednesday night service, Sunday night service, prayer group, whatever you have to do to get plugged in so that you do not go back to the trash you used to be a part of.

01:39:01.630 --> 01:39:02.000
So get plugged in, get excited about your new life in Christ.

01:39:02.000 --> 01:39:08.400
If you do not have a Bible, my wife and I—I think she is almost caught up.

01:39:08.400 --> 01:39:12.027
Bless her heart.

01:39:12.027 --> 01:39:19.600
She has been trying really hard to get all these Bibles out to you all.

01:39:19.600 --> 01:39:38.080
If you do not have a Bible and you just gave your heart to Jesus Christ, now did you hear what I said?

01:39:56.617 --> 01:39:57.051
This is not for your cousin's cousin's cousin to have a Bible.

01:39:57.051 --> 01:40:04.571
Our ministry cannot afford to support all the salvations that come in here.

01:40:04.571 --> 01:41:12.107
If you have never accepted Jesus Christ and you just did, and you do not have a Bible, we want to buy you a Bible for free.

01:41:12.107 --> 01:41:21.075
Not for your ministry for you to give out 100 Bibles to all the people on the streets.

01:41:21.075 --> 01:41:23.977
I am not trying to rant.

01:41:23.977 --> 01:41:30.560
I am just trying to tell you that is where we are right now.

01:41:30.560 --> 01:41:36.421
Until the Lord expands us, we will buy you your Bible.

01:41:36.421 --> 01:41:46.791
Now, you have to give your address and where to send it, and we will send it to you.

01:41:46.791 --> 01:41:48.582
We will not solicit you.

01:41:48.582 --> 01:41:51.720
We do not want to bother you.

01:41:51.720 --> 01:41:58.820
We just want to tell you welcome to the family and we love you.

01:42:43.474 --> 01:42:43.760
A Bible will come.

01:42:43.760 --> 01:42:46.210
Amazon banned us from doing it.

01:42:46.210 --> 01:44:10.663
We cannot send it to you from Amazon anymore because they took away our account from that because they thought we were dropshipping, and I did not understand what that was, but they did.

01:44:10.663 --> 01:44:19.166
So Diana said, "Oh, we got in trouble, so we have to go in a different direction through another book company," but we found a way to do it.

01:44:19.166 --> 01:44:24.898
All glory to Jesus, so we will send you your Bible for free just to love on you.

01:44:43.199 --> 01:44:43.546
It will be a New King James Version or a King James.

01:44:43.546 --> 01:44:52.199
We just love you, so thankful that you are here tonight.

01:44:52.199 --> 01:45:30.420
Welcome to the family.

01:45:30.420 --> 01:45:42.426
All heaven is rejoicing, and all hell is saying we lost a good sinner tonight.

01:45:42.426 --> 01:45:46.758
How many got saved?

01:45:46.758 --> 01:45:56.293
Did we have anybody give their heart to Jesus Christ?

01:45:56.293 --> 01:45:59.728
If not, that is all right.

01:45:59.728 --> 01:46:02.200
Oh, we had 56.

01:46:02.200 --> 01:46:15.270
Well, praise the Lord.

01:46:15.280 --> 01:46:20.701
All 56 of you that gave your heart to Jesus Christ, welcome to the family.

01:46:20.701 --> 01:46:30.890
That is exciting, and we will have a lot more throughout the week or when they watch this.

01:46:35.055 --> 01:46:35.679
So, let us go pray.

01:46:35.679 --> 01:46:41.680
I know I have kept you late, but it is not too late.

01:46:41.680 --> 01:46:45.199
Father, we just lift up the body before you.

01:46:45.199 --> 01:47:26.790
We thank you, Lord, for all that you have done and all that you are going to do.

01:47:26.800 --> 01:47:45.280
Father, we thank you, Lord, that we are healed and whole by your stripes.

01:48:13.863 --> 01:48:28.687
The Bible says that you were wounded for our transgressions.

01:48:28.687 --> 01:48:45.440
You were bruised for our iniquities.

01:48:47.810 --> 01:49:00.736
The chastisement of our peace was upon you, and with your stripes, Lord, we are healed.

01:49:00.736 --> 01:49:02.204
We believe.

01:49:02.204 --> 01:49:12.930
We receive healing and wholeness and wellness in the name of Jesus.

01:49:12.930 --> 01:49:41.216
That by your stripes, Lord, we are healed and whole in our bodies.

01:49:41.216 --> 01:49:49.227
We receive it in the name of Jesus.

01:49:57.155 --> 01:50:06.372
And we take this by faith, knowing that Jesus took it all.

01:50:06.372 --> 01:50:14.473
Jesus paid it all.

01:50:14.473 --> 01:50:19.849
Jesus took it in his body.

01:50:19.849 --> 01:50:22.240
He did it all for us.

01:50:22.240 --> 01:50:28.010
According to Galatians 3, Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

01:50:28.010 --> 01:50:39.040
Earlier, we were reading about the blessing, but the curse is all the way through Deuteronomy 28, and we are redeemed from the curses of it.

01:50:39.040 --> 01:51:35.920
So Father, I thank you, Lord, for the blessing and for your healing power that flows on the inside of us richly by faith in Jesus' mighty name.

01:51:35.920 --> 01:53:21.786
Lord, we take the blood and we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:53:21.786 --> 01:53:26.285
We thank you for the blood.

01:53:46.960 --> 01:53:47.280
It has never lost its power.

01:53:47.280 --> 01:53:58.060
Father, I thank you, Lord, that it reaches to the highest mountain and it flows to the lowest valley.

01:54:01.999 --> 01:54:07.400
The blood of Jesus Christ, it is over us, and it cleanses us from all unrighteousness.

01:54:07.400 --> 01:54:10.663
We thank you, Lord, for the blood.

01:54:10.663 --> 01:54:12.686
We make much of that blood.

01:54:12.686 --> 01:54:23.828
We apply the blood over our eyes, Father, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:54:23.828 --> 01:54:24.994
I believe.

01:54:24.994 --> 01:54:28.623
I yield to the anointing of the prophetic.

01:54:28.623 --> 01:54:29.679
I yield.

01:54:29.679 --> 01:54:31.630
I thank you, Lord.

01:54:31.630 --> 01:54:47.600
If there is anything you want to show us of that which is to come, for Father, you told us in your Word the Holy Spirit would show us that which is to come.

01:54:58.719 --> 01:54:59.119
We thank you, Lord.

01:54:59.119 --> 01:55:08.664
We have this treasure in earthen vessels, and the excellency is the power known of you and not of us.

01:55:08.664 --> 01:55:18.639
We apply the blood of Jesus over us right now in Jesus' name and we give you much praise, Father, in Jesus' mighty name.

01:55:18.639 --> 01:55:18.977
Amen.

01:55:18.977 --> 01:55:20.445
Now, I anointed my head with oil.

01:55:20.445 --> 01:55:23.219
I want you to fix your collar.

01:55:23.219 --> 01:55:24.810
Oh, thanks.

01:55:24.810 --> 01:55:26.690
Thank you all.

01:55:26.690 --> 01:55:27.849
I appreciate that.

01:55:41.154 --> 01:55:41.429
We have to look nice for Jesus.

01:55:41.429 --> 01:55:47.421
I do not want to be a distraction.

01:55:47.421 --> 01:55:50.120
Father, we give you praise.

01:55:50.120 --> 01:55:54.537
Now, I want you to thank him for everything he has done for you today.

01:56:04.011 --> 01:56:04.263
You just thank him.

01:56:04.263 --> 01:56:08.753
Thank him for the birds, whatever it may be, finances, whatever.

01:56:08.753 --> 01:56:09.348
Okay?

01:56:24.400 --> 01:56:24.702
I want you to give him praise and glory like Paul and Silas.

01:56:24.702 --> 01:56:31.679
Give him praise in the midnight hour, for whenever they gave praise, the walls began to shake, and they were freed from their captivity.

01:56:31.679 --> 01:56:39.493
Father, we give you praise and glory for all that you have done and all that you continue to do.

01:56:43.360 --> 01:56:43.840
I thank you, Father, for the blood that covers us.

01:56:43.840 --> 01:56:46.823
Father, I thank you for your healings.

01:58:36.748 --> 01:58:37.897
I thank you for the manifestations of the glory tonight.

01:58:42.492 --> 01:58:56.176
I thank you for my wife and my children.

01:58:56.176 --> 01:59:19.856
I thank you, Lord, that you said in Psalms 91 that a thousand shall fall at my side and 10,000 at my right hand, but nothing shall come nigh me.

01:59:28.702 --> 01:59:29.058
I thank you, Lord, for my home.

01:59:47.173 --> 01:59:47.787
I thank you, Lord, for the roof over my head.

01:59:47.787 --> 01:59:59.520
I thank you that my bills are paid, the electric, my water, my gas, my car payments.

01:59:59.520 --> 02:00:03.474
Father, you are so good to us.

02:00:03.474 --> 02:00:07.520
Thank you, Lord, for all that you have provided.

02:00:07.520 --> 02:00:13.399
Thank you, Lord, that we have clothes on our back and a new shirt.

02:00:13.399 --> 02:00:16.990
Father, I am so thankful for my shirt.

02:00:16.990 --> 02:00:24.069
I am so thankful, Father, that I have something to wear that is nice for the people.

02:00:44.960 --> 02:00:46.610
Thank you, Lord, you provided for it.

02:00:46.610 --> 02:01:05.400
I thank you, Lord, that you gave a roof over my head, that Father, I am not out in the cold, and that you gave us a place so we are not out in the rain.

02:01:05.400 --> 02:01:07.779
God, you gave us a good place.

02:01:07.779 --> 02:01:16.639
Father, I thank you, Lord, that we have a bed to sleep in, and Father, that we have covers to cover ourselves up with.

02:01:16.639 --> 02:02:01.040
Father, we are so grateful for the fan that blows on us as we do the broadcast.

02:02:01.040 --> 02:02:14.640
Father, we are so grateful for the flowers that are about to bloom in the spring, and for the trees that are about to have leaves and that will have longer days and shorter nights.

02:02:14.640 --> 02:02:16.080
Father, I love the spring.

02:02:16.860 --> 02:02:17.400
I love the summer.

02:02:48.460 --> 02:02:48.730
I love that the weather is warming up, and that the daffodils are about to bloom and the tulips are about to come out.

02:02:56.800 --> 02:02:58.514
Father, we thank you for the redbud trees that are about to bloom.

02:02:58.514 --> 02:03:01.240
God, we are so grateful for the trees.

02:03:11.942 --> 02:03:12.388
We are so grateful that the birds are going to start to migrate back north.

02:03:26.239 --> 02:03:26.469
Father, we are so grateful for all the birds, and that the baby deer are about to give birth.

02:03:39.120 --> 02:03:39.760
The fawns will be on the earth.

02:03:44.411 --> 02:03:44.823
We are so grateful for the fawns.

02:03:59.920 --> 02:04:00.274
We are so grateful for the spawning bass that are about to spawn in the spring.

02:04:09.611 --> 02:04:13.679
We are so grateful for all that you have given us in nature, the squirrels, the chipmunks, and all the beautiful things you have given us, Lord.

02:04:13.679 --> 02:04:27.070
Father, we are so grateful for the tires on our car that get us from point A to point B.

02:04:27.070 --> 02:04:44.080
We are so grateful that we have a stereo in our car that we can turn up as loud as we want and listen to praise and worship music.

02:04:44.080 --> 02:04:52.719
Father, I am so grateful that we live in a free country right now.

02:04:52.719 --> 02:04:56.559
We are thankful for President Trump.

02:04:56.559 --> 02:04:58.320
We are grateful for Congress.

02:04:58.320 --> 02:05:26.049
We are grateful for the judges, the Supreme Court judges, because there are more conservative than there are liberal judges.

02:05:26.049 --> 02:05:34.080
Father, I thank you, Lord, in the name of Jesus, that you are turning this nation around.

02:06:03.920 --> 02:06:04.210
We are one nation under God.

